ACCORDION_QUESTION_1: How does the app help me find new products?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: Our app uses advanced algorithms and user preferences to curate a personalized selection of new and trending products across various categories, ensuring you discover items that match your interests and needs.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_2: Is the app free to use?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: Yes, the basic version of our app is completely free to use. We also offer a premium subscription with additional features for those who want an enhanced product discovery experience.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: Can I purchase products directly through the app?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: While our app focuses on product discovery, we provide direct links to trusted retailers where you can make purchases. We ensure a seamless transition from discovery to purchase for your convenience.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: How often are new products added to the app?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: We update our product database daily, adding the latest and most innovative items from various markets and industries. This ensures you always have access to the newest products and trends.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_1: How does the product discovery app work?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Our app uses advanced algorithms and user preferences to suggest new and exciting products tailored to your interests. Simply browse, like, or skip items to refine your recommendations.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_2: Is the app free to use?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: Yes, the basic version of our app is completely free. We also offer a premium subscription with additional features for enhanced product discovery.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: Can I purchase products directly through the app?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: While we don't handle transactions directly, our app provides links to trusted retailers where you can purchase the products you discover. We aim to make the buying process as seamless as possible.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: How often are new products added to the app?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: We update our product database daily to ensure you always have access to the latest and most innovative items across various categories.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: Can I share product discoveries with friends?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: Absolutely! Our app includes social sharing features that allow you to easily share your favorite product finds with friends and family through various social media platforms or direct messaging.
